    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i just had the weirdest thing happen. i was sitting in the library and literally out of nowhere i got this headache that felt like a freaking bolt of lightning hit my head. like it was so intense for a second i actually felt sick but it passed pretty fast after like a minute. now im just feeling kinda foggy and weird. u think i just need some water or maybe an ibuprofen? its probably just dehydration or something right?",
