      "content": "wait a mini stroke?? that sounds way too intense. i dont think i can get to an er right now, i'm stuck in this library and i don't have anyone to drive me and urber is like 30 mins away. i really don't want to make a huge deal out of nothing if it's just a weird headache. is there like anything i can take right now to just calm my blood pressure or something to make the dizziness go away so i can just sleep it off? maybe some extra strong aspirin or something?",
