    "summary": "The user describes a sudden, \"thunderclap\" style headache and dizziness. The assistant initially misdiagnoses it as a migraine aura, but upon further clarification of the symptoms, correctly identifies the high-risk nature of the episode and provides urgent advice to seek emergency medical care while specifically warning against taking aspirin.",
